<a href="/articles/24768.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/24768/indexMediumPc2/24768.jpg?1459397515" alt="「这世界」房租太贵，他在朋友家里搭了一个木头小窝">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/5/medium/5.png?1411569637" alt="城市">
			<span>城市</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">「这世界」房租太贵，他在朋友家里搭了一个木头小窝</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-31 13:18:54 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">1</span>
